thread.title_full: Juncker: 'Greek negotiation position will be dramatically weakened by a NO vote' | EurActiv

author: euractiv.com
title: Juncker: 'Greek negotiation position will be dramatically weakened by a NO vote'
text:
Two days before Greece votes in a referendum on the most recent EU bailout deal, Commission President Jean-Claude Juncker said, â€œIf the Greeks vote no, their position will be very weak."
Juncker was speaking at a press conference in Luxembourg on Friday (3 July) alongside Prime Minister Xavier Bettel, who presented the priorities of the Luxembourgish Presidency of the European Council.
